                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI'>KEY INSIGHTS</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='7'>• ATM infrastructure is the strongest contributor to the Shadow Economy Score, followed by Electricity Consumption and MSME activity.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='7'>• High-risk districts are primarily concentrated in economically active urban and industrial regions.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='7'>• Districts with high Nightlight intensity but comparatively low financial inclusion exhibit elevated informal economy risk.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='7'>• Select any district on the map or scatter plot to interactively explore its risk profile across all visualizations.</run>
