                <formatted-text>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI'>Executive Insights</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'>• MSME activity contributes </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'>56.9%</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'> of the composite risk index.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'>• Districts naturally form </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'>4 economic clusters</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'> using PCA + K-Means.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'>• Higher Nightlight intensity generally corresponds with stronger economic activity.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'>• Several states show statistically significant variability, indicating uneven informal economic concentration.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='8'>• Formalization remains weak in high economic activity regions.</run>
                </formatted-text>
